  "response": "As of my last update, several in-ear earphones under Rs. 1000 are well-regarded for their quality, sound performance, and durability. Here are a couple of options that you might consider:\n\n1. **Mi Dual Driver In-Ear Earphones**: These come with dual drivers that provide a good bass response and overall balanced sound quality. They are comfortable to wear and offer a decent build quality for the price.\n\n2. **Realme Buds 2**: Known for their good sound quality and bass-heavy performance, these earphones also come with a durable build and a tangle-free cable. They have a nice ergonomic design for comfort.\n\n3. **boAt Bassheads 100**: These are popular for their appealing design and decent sound quality, particularly focused on bass. They are lightweight and come with a variety of color options.\n\n4. **Redmi Earphones**: Another great option from Xiaomi, known for decent sound quality, comfort, and a good build.\n\nWhen selecting earphones, it's essential to consider factors like sound quality, durability, and comfort. Prices may fluctuate, so it's a good idea to check current prices and user reviews before making a purchase.",
